* Opening bids

1C = !F, 18+ HCP or 2+!c 12+ HCP
1D = 5+!d or 4!d(441), 12--17 HCP
1H = 5+!h, 11--17 HCP
1S = 5+!s, 11--17 HCP
1N = 2--4!s, 2--4!h, 2--6!d, 2--6!c, 15--17 HCP
2C = !PRE, 4+!s, 4+!h, 4--10 HCP
2D = !PRE, 6+M, 4--10 HCP
2M = PRE, 5#, 4--10 HCP
2N = !UNT, 5+!d, 5+!c, 4--10 HCP
3X = PRE, 7+#, 4--10 HCP
3N = !Gambling, SOL 7+m, 0--1 outside CTRL
4C = !Namyats, S-SOL 7+!h, 4.5--5.5 NLTC
4D = !Namyats, S-SOL 7+!s, 4.5--5.5 NLTC
4M = PRE, good 7+#
4N = !UNT, 6+!d, 6+!c, 11--15 HCP

** The notrump ladder

- *12--14*: 1!c-1!d-1M
- *15--17*: 1NT
- *18--20*: 1!c-1!d-1NT
- *21--23*: 1!c-1!d-2NT
- *24+*: 1!c-1!d-2!d-2!h-2NT

